              "path": "packages/framework/SKILL.md"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": " is the entry contract. The rest of the package is the material it can load: a pointer-only reference area, intent cookbooks, imperative standards, task workflows, adaptable document templates, and mounting instructions. There is no "
